t\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δεινίας Κηφισοδότου Βουτάδης\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δεινίας\">Δεινίας\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κηφισοδότου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Κηφισοδότου\">Κηφ[ισο]δότου\u003C/span>\u003C/span> Βουτάδης\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>θεσμοθετήσας ἐπὶ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φειδοστράτου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φειδοστράτου\">Φειδοστράτου\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ἄρχοντος ἀνέθηκεν \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[ἡ βουλή] ὁ δῆμος \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Giorgia Capra\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δεινίας Κηφισοδότου Βουτάδης\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δεινίας\">ΔΕΙΝΙΑΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κηφισοδότου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Κηφισοδότου\">ΚΗΦ[...]ΔΟΤΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΒΟΥΤΑΔΗΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΘΕΣΜΟΘΕΤΗΣΑΣΕΠΙ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φειδοστράτου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φειδοστράτου\">ΦΕΙΔΟΣΤΡΑΤΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΑΡΧΟΝΤΟΣΑΝΕΘΗΚΕΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[......]ΟΔΗΜΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text of IG\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\" https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1030-5679\">Giorgia Capra\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Deinias son of Kephisodotos of Boutadai, who was thesmothete when Pheidostratos was archon, dedicated this. (In crown, on the left) The Council. (In crown, on the right) The People.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\" https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1030-5679\">Giorgia Capra\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Deinias figlio di Kephisodotos di Boutadai, che era tesmoteta durante l'arcontato di Pheidostratos, dedicò questo. (In corona, a sinistra) Il consiglio. (In corona, a destra) Il popolo.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The inscription appears already in the museum inventory of 1885, described as 'prov. incerta', and was previously observed in the earlier version of the museum by Julius Schubring in the 1860s. There is no record of how it came to be in Sicily, and as Manganaro obserfves, it most likely arrived as ballast stone in a ship (at some date prior to c.1860).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 02/03(2).3.1.2855 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000420\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000420\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> 02/03(3).4.1.99 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000413\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000413\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Schubring 1861-1867 672 no. 7, tab. no.7 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001601\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001601\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Libertini 1929 121 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001872\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001872\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1965 205 tav. LXXV.1 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[231,234,237,240,243,245,248,251,254],{"id":232,"html":233},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Giorgia Capra\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δεινίας Κηφισοδότου Βουτάδης\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δεινίας\">Δεινίας\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κηφισοδότου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Κηφισοδότου\">Κηφ[ισο]δότου\u003C/span>\u003C/span> Βουτάδης\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>θεσμοθετήσας ἐπὶ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φειδοστράτου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φειδοστράτου\">Φειδοστράτου\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ἄρχοντος ἀνέθηκεν \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[ἡ βουλή] ὁ δῆμος \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Giorgia Capra\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δεινίας Κηφισοδότου Βουτάδης\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δεινίας\">ΔΕΙΝΙΑΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κηφισοδότου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Κηφισοδότου\">ΚΗΦ[...]ΔΟΤΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΒΟΥΤΑΔΗΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΘΕΣΜΟΘΕΤΗΣΑΣΕΠΙ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φειδοστράτου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φειδοστράτου\">ΦΕΙΔΟΣΤΡΑΤΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΑΡΧΟΝΤΟΣΑΝΕΘΗΚΕΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[......]ΟΔΗΜΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":235,"html":236},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>",{"id":238,"html":239},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text of IG\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":241,"html":242},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\" https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1030-5679\">Giorgia Capra\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Deinias son of Kephisodotos of Boutadai, who was thesmothete when Pheidostratos was archon, dedicated this. (In crown, on the left) The Council. (In crown, on the right) The People.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":241,"html":244},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\" https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1030-5679\">Giorgia Capra\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Deinias figlio di Kephisodotos di Boutadai, che era tesmoteta durante l'arcontato di Pheidostratos, dedicò questo. (In corona, a sinistra) Il consiglio. (In corona, a destra) Il popolo.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":246,"html":247},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The inscription appears already in the museum inventory of 1885, described as 'prov. incerta', and was previously observed in the earlier version of the museum by Julius Schubring in the 1860s. There is no record of how it came to be in Sicily, and as Manganaro obserfves, it most likely arrived as ballast stone in a ship (at some date prior to c.1860).\u003C/p>  ",{"id":249,"html":250},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 02/03(2).3.1.2855 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000420\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000420\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> 02/03(3).4.1.99 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000413\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000413\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Schubring 1861-1867 672 no. 7, tab. no.7 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001601\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001601\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Libertini 1929 121 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001872\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001872\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1965 205 tav. LXXV.1 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":252,"html":253},"handnote"," Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    ",{"id":255,"html":256},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[258,260,263,264],{"html":259},"Text encoding: Giorgia Capra",{"id":261,"lang":114,"html":262},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δεινίας Κηφισοδότου Βουτάδης\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δεινίας\">Δεινίας\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κηφισοδότου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Κηφισοδότου\">Κηφ[ισο]δότου\u003C/span>\u003C/span> Βουτάδης\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>θεσμοθετήσας ἐπὶ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φειδοστράτου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φειδοστράτου\">Φειδοστράτου\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ἄρχοντος ἀνέθηκεν \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[ἡ βουλή] ὁ δῆμος \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":259},{"id":265,"lang":114,"html":266},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-